'''蟲草素'''，或者是 '''3'-脫氧腺苷'''，是[[腺嘌呤|腺嘌呤]][[核糖|核糖]]核苷的衍生物，两者的差别在于前者在核糖的3位上比后者少一个氧。该物质最早是从[[真菌|真菌]]虫草(Cordyceps militaris)<ref>{{cite journal | author = Cunningham, K. G. | author2 = Manson, W. | author3 = Spring, F. S. | author4 = Hutchinson, S. A. | last-author-amp = yes | year = 1950 | title = Cordycepin, a Metabolic Product isolated from Cultures of Cordyceps militaris (Linn.) Link. | journal = Nature | volume = 166 | pages = 949 | url = http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v166/n4231/abs/166949a0.html | doi = 10.1038/166949a0 | pmid = 14796634 | access-date = 2018-03-05 | archive-date = 2017-03-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170330235209/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v166/n4231/abs/166949a0.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>中获得的，但现在已经能通过化学方法合成。

因為蟲草素相似於腺嘌呤脱氧核糖核苷（缺的氧在2位上面），许多酶无法将两者区分开来。所以，虫草素可以参与一些特定的生物化学反应（例如，被掺入到RNA分子中，从而导致其合成的提前终止）。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Siev, M., Weinberg, R. and Penman, S. | year = 1969 | title = The selective interruption of nucleolar RNA synthesis in HeLa cells by cordycepin | journal = J. Cell Biol. | volume = 41 | pages = 510–520 | url = http://www.jcb.org/cgi/reprint/41/2/510 | doi = 10.1083/jcb.41.2.510 | pmid = 5783871 | issue = 2 | pmc = 2107749 | access-date = 2014-09-13 | archive-date = 2007-09-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070929093016/http://www.jcb.org/cgi/reprint/41/2/510 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="pmid23118416">{{cite journal| author=Kondrashov A, Meijer HA, Barthet-Barateig A, Parker HN, Khurshid A, Tessier S et al.| title=Inhibition of polyadenylation reduces inflammatory gene induction. | journal=RNA | year= 2012 | volume=  18| issue=  12| pages=  2236–50| pmid=23118416 | doi=10.1261/rna.032391.112 | pmc= 3504674| url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=23118416  }} </ref>

虫草素在体外对一些白血病细胞系表现出[[细胞毒性|细胞毒性]]，至少有一项虫草素作为[[白血病|白血病]]治疗的临床试验正在进行中<ref>{{cite web|author=National Cancer Institute|title=Definition of cordycepin|url=http://www.cancer.gov/publications/dictionaries/cancer-drug?cdrid=42667|website=NCI Drug Dictionary|accessdate=21 December 2015|archive-date=2018-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125122218/https://www.cancer.gov/publications/dictionaries/cancer-drug?CdrID=42667|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

虫草素已被发现在[[抑郁症|抑郁症]]的[[模式生物|动物模型]]中产生快速，强健的丙咪嗪类[[抗抑郁药|抗抑郁药]]作用，并且这些作用与丙咪嗪类似，都依赖于{{le|AMPA受体|AMPA receptor}}信号传导的增强<ref name="LiHou2016">{{cite journal|last1=Li|first1=Bai|last2=Hou|first2=Yangyang|last3=Zhu|first3=Ming|last4=Bao|first4=Hongkun|last5=Nie|first5=Jun|last6=Zhang|first6=Grace Y.|last7=Shan|first7=Liping|last8=Yao|first8=Yao|last9=Du|first9=Kai|last10=Yang|first10=Hongju|last11=Li|first11=Meizhang|last12=Zheng|first12=Bingrong|last13=Xu|first13=Xiufeng|last14=Xiao|first14=Chunjie|last15=Du|first15=Jing|title=3’-Deoxyadenosine (Cordycepin) Produces a Rapid and Robust Antidepressant Effect via Enhancing Prefrontal AMPA Receptor Signaling Pathway|journal=International Journal of Neuropsychopharmacology|volume=19|issue=4|year=2016|pages=pyv112|issn=1461-1457|doi=10.1093/ijnp/pyv112}}</ref>。

蟲草素在近年來更有研究發現可以有效地治療第一型及[[第二型糖尿病|第二型糖尿病]]，也有發現單磷酸化的蟲草素構型類似於AMP，因此能作用於[[AMPK|AMPK]]，而具有成為非小細胞肺癌[[標靶藥物|標靶藥物]]的潛力。<ref>{{cite journal |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20724804/ |title=Cordycepin prevents hyperlipidemia in hamsters fed a high-fat diet via activation of AMP-activated protein kinase |first1=Peng |last1=Guo |first2=Qu |last2=Kai |first3=Jian |last3=Gao |first4=Ze-qin |last4=Lian |first5=Chong-ming |last5=Wu |first6=Cheng-ai |last6=Wu |first7=Hai-bo |last7=Zhu |year=2010 |journal=[[J_Pharmacol_Sci|J Pharmacol Sci]]. |volume=113 |issue=4 |pages=395-403 |doi=10.1254/jphs.10041fp |pmid=20724804 |access-date=2021-04-18 |language=en |archive-date=2021-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419144942/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20724804/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

